{1 attribute-anchors}
- Spec: {!page-"feature-attribute-anchors"}
- Core: {!Oystermark.Vault.Index.extract_attr_ids} (collection),
  {!Oystermark.Vault.Resolve.resolve} ([Attr]/[Curr_attr] cases).
- Consumers: {!module-Lsp_lib.Go_to_definition} and
  {!module-Lsp_lib.Find_references} (attribute anchor targets).
- Test: {!module-Lsp_lib.Go_to_definition.test},
  {!module-Lsp_lib.Find_references.test}, and
  [Oystermark.Vault.Index]'s [extract_attr_ids] expect test.
- Column precision: go-to-definition returns a [(line, character)]
  position; inline anchors land mid-line. Derivation:
  {!Lsp_lib.Util.position_of_textloc}, spec
  {!page-"feature-go-to-definition".target_position}. The [character] is
  a byte offset (ASCII-correct) pending {!page-"feature-utf16-positions"}.
- Follow-ups (not yet done): attribute-anchor embed/hover section
  extraction, duplicate-id diagnostics, and attribute ids in completion.
